=== 外交以及內政 ===
在西班牙的"巴塞隆納5 月事件"之後他一度只任命了左派人士進入政府中而没有任命'''全國勞工聯盟和勞動者總聯盟''',當時引趗了兩黨的不滿和西方兩國的猜忌;<ref>{{Cite web|title=Juan Negrín López {{!}} prime minister of Spain|url=https://www.britannica.com/biography/Juan-Negrin-Lopez|accessdate=2020-12-06|work=Encyclopedia Britannica|language=en|archive-date=2021-04-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210426051914/https://www.britannica.com/biography/Juan-Negrin-Lopez|dead-url=no}}</ref>而兩黨發表聲明譴責共和國政府"反革命",而全國勞工聯盟更加在1937年5月25在國家委員會上不但形容西班牙共產黨是反革命政黨<ref>{{Cite book|chapter=46  The Negrín Government and the Reaction of the Libertarian Movement|url=http://dx.doi.org/10.5149/northcarolina/9781469624464.001.0001|publisher=University of North Carolina Press|date=2015-09-28|isbn=978-1-4696-2446-4|first=Burnett|last=Bolloten|first2=Stanley G.|last2=Payne|first3=George|last3=Esenwein|title=The Spanish Civil War : Revolution and Counterrevolution|year=2015|location=USA|pages=P.484}}</ref>,他們更加形容西班牙共產黨是:<blockquote>"close collaboration with the bourgeois republican parties and right-wing Socialists," had brought to fruition the "political maneuver" that had culminated in the "provocation in Barcelona" <ref>{{Cite book|chapter=46 The Negrín Government and the Reaction of the Libertarian Movement|url=http://dx.doi.org/10.5149/northcarolina/9781469624464.001.0001|publisher=University of North Carolina Press|date=2015-09-28|isbn=978-1-4696-2446-4|first=Burnett|last=Bolloten|first2=Stanley G.|last2=Payne|first3=George|last3=Esenwein|title=The Spanish Civil War: Revolution and Counterrevolution|year=2015|location=USA|pages=p.484}}</ref></blockquote>,而同年的蘇聯駐英國大使形容當時的胡安.內格林政府:<blockquote>"the new Premier understood the vital need to cooperate with the Communist party and did not grieve unduly that the Anarchosyndicalists refused to come into his cabinet.He boldly slashed the numbers of ministers from 18 to 9. This made the govern-ment more compact and functional, and, most important, the ratio of Commu-nists within it was considerably higher."<ref>{{Cite book|chapter=46  The Negrín Government and the Reaction of the Libertarian Movement|url=http://dx.doi.org/10.5149/northcarolina/9781469624464.001.0001|publisher=University of North Carolina Press|date=2015-09-28|isbn=978-1-4696-2446-4|first=Burnett|last=Bolloten|first2=Stanley G.|last2=Payne|first3=George|last3=Esenwein|title=The Spanish Civil War : Revolution and Counterrevolution|year=2015|location=美國|pages=484}}</ref></blockquote>當胡安.內格林在1939年重新任命'''全國勞工聯盟和勞動者總聯盟兩黨的成員進入政府之後兩黨就對這個決定感到鼓舞。'''<ref>{{Cite book|chapter=55  The Second Negrín Government. Communist Predominance in the Army.|url=http://dx.doi.org/10.5149/northcarolina/9781469624464.001.0001|publisher=University of North Carolina Press|date=2015-09-28|isbn=978-1-4696-2446-4|first=Burnett|last=Bolloten|first2=Stanley G.|last2=Payne|first3=George|last3=Esenwein|title=The Spanish Civil War : Revolution and Counterrevolution|year=2015|location=USA|pages=586}}</ref>

== 流亡生涯及死去(1939年3月31日-1956月12日 ) ==
1939年3月31 日，隨著戰況每況愈下,共和國潰不成軍,他決定辭職流亡法國,德國在1940年6月佔領了法國之後，他又流亡英國，戰後返回法國（西班牙佛朗哥政權在二次大戰之後仍然存在），最後在1956.11.12在法國巴黎死去。<ref name=":0" /><ref name=":3" />

